CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: LiveWire Group Inc is an all-electric vehicle company. It sells electric vehicles and related parts and accessories and apparel in the United States and certain international markets. LiveWire generates revenue from the sale of electric motorcycles, electric balance bikes, related P&A, and apparel.
